{% comment %}
  FAQ page section — accordion style
{% endcomment %}

<div class="info-page-header">
  <div class="page-container">
    <span class="section-label">Help Centre</span>
    <h1>Frequently Asked Questions</h1>
    <p class="info-page-header__lead">Everything you need to know about ordering, sizing, shipping, and returns.</p>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="faq-page page-container">

  <nav class="faq-nav" aria-label="FAQ categories">
    <a href="#sizing" class="faq-nav__link">Sizing</a>
    <a href="#orders" class="faq-nav__link">Orders &amp; Payment</a>
    <a href="#shipping-faq" class="faq-nav__link">Shipping</a>
    <a href="#returns-faq" class="faq-nav__link">Returns</a>
    <a href="#care" class="faq-nav__link">Care</a>
  </nav>

  <div class="faq-sections">

    <section class="faq-section" id="sizing">
      <h2>Sizing</h2>
      <div class="faq-list">
        <details class="faq-item">
          <summary>How do I find my size?</summary>
          <div class="faq-answer">
            <p>Use our <a href="/pages/size-guide">Size Guide</a> for full measurements. In general, our pieces run true to size. If you're between sizes, we recommend sizing up for a relaxed fit — especially in our linen collection.</p>
          </div>
        </details>
        <details class="faq-item">
          <summary>Do you use EU or UK sizing?</summary>
          <div class="faq-answer">
            <p>We use both. Our product pages show size labels in UK and EU (e.g. UK 8 / EU 36). Our <a href="/pages/size-guide">Size Guide</a> includes a full conversion chart.</p>
          </div>
        </details>
        <details class="faq-item">
          <summary>Are your pieces true to size?</summary>
          <div class="faq-answer">
            <p>Yes, generally. Our swimwear is designed for a close fit, so if you prefer more coverage, size up. Our linen pieces are intentionally relaxed — they're sized to fit comfortably, not tightly.</p>
          </div>
        </details>
        <details class="faq-item">
          <summary>What sizes do you stock?</summary>
          <div class="faq-answer">
            <p>We currently stock XS to XL across most styles. Size availability varies by product — check the size selector on each product page for current stock.</p>
          </div>
        </details>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="faq-section" id="orders">
      <h2>Orders &amp; Payment</h2>
      <div class="faq-list">
        <details class="faq-item">
          <summary>What payment methods do you accept?</summary>
          <div class="faq-answer">
            <p>We accept:</p>
            <ul>
              <li><strong>All markets:</strong> Visa, Mastercard, American Express, Apple Pay, Google Pay</li>
              <li><strong>UK:</strong> Klarna (Buy Now Pay Later)</li>
              <li><strong>France:</strong> Carte Bancaire, PayPal, Klarna</li>
              <li><strong>Netherlands:</strong> iDEAL, PayPal, Klarna</li>
              <li><strong>Germany &amp; Belgium:</strong> Bancontact, PayPal, Klarna</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </details>
        <details class="faq-item">
          <summary>Can I modify or cancel my order?</summary>
          <div class="faq-answer">
            <p>Orders can be modified or cancelled within 1 hour of placement. After that, they enter our fulfilment process. Email <a href="mailto:hello@tcpclothing.com">hello@tcpclothing.com</a> as quickly as possible and we'll do our best.</p>
          </div>
        </details>
        <details class="faq-item">
          <summary>Will I get an order confirmation?</summary>
          <div class="faq-answer">
            <p>Yes — you'll receive an email confirmation immediately after purchase, followed by a shipping confirmation with tracking once your order is dispatched.</p>
          </div>
        </details>
        <details class="faq-item">
          <summary>Is it safe to pay on your site?</summary>
          <div class="faq-answer">
            <p>Yes. Our store is powered by Shopify, which uses industry-standard SSL encryption. We never store your card details — all payments are processed securely via Shopify Payments.</p>
          </div>
        </details>
        <details class="faq-item">
          <summary>Do prices include VAT?</summary>
          <div class="faq-answer">
            <p>All prices shown include applicable VAT for your region: 20% for UK and France, 21% for Netherlands. Your invoice will show the VAT amount separately.</p>
          </div>
        </details>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="faq-section" id="shipping-faq">
      <h2>Shipping</h2>
      <div class="faq-list">
        <details class="faq-item">
          <summary>How long does delivery take?</summary>
          <div class="faq-answer">
            <p>Delivery times depend on your location:</p>
            <ul>
              <li><strong>UK:</strong> 3–5 business days (standard), 1–2 days (express)</li>
              <li><strong>France:</strong> 4–6 business days (standard), 2–3 days (express)</li>
              <li><strong>Netherlands:</strong> 3–5 business days (standard), 2–3 days (express)</li>
              <li><strong>Rest of EU:</strong> 5–7 business days</li>
            </ul>
            <p>See our full <a href="/pages/shipping">Shipping &amp; Returns</a> page for rates and all countries.</p>
          </div>
        </details>
        <details class="faq-item">
          <summary>Do you offer free shipping?</summary>
          <div class="faq-answer">
            <p>Yes! Free standard shipping on orders over £60 (UK), €70 (France, Netherlands, Germany, Belgium), and €80 (Spain, Italy).</p>
          </div>
        </details>
        <details class="faq-item">
          <summary>Can I track my order?</summary>
          <div class="faq-answer">
            <p>Yes. Once your order ships, you'll receive a tracking number by email. You can also view your order status in your <a href="/account">account</a>.</p>
          </div>
        </details>
        <details class="faq-item">
          <summary>Do you ship outside Europe?</summary>
          <div class="faq-answer">
            <p>Currently we ship to UK, France, Netherlands, Germany, Belgium, Spain, Italy, Sweden, and Denmark. We're working on expanding to more markets — sign up to our newsletter to be notified.</p>
          </div>
        </details>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="faq-section" id="returns-faq">
      <h2>Returns</h2>
      <div class="faq-list">
        <details class="faq-item">
          <summary>How long do I have to return?</summary>
          <div class="faq-answer">
            <p>You have 14 days from the delivery date to return any item in its original, unworn, unwashed condition with tags attached.</p>
          </div>
        </details>
        <details class="faq-item">
          <summary>How do I start a return?</summary>
          <div class="faq-answer">
            <p>Email <a href="mailto:hello@tcpclothing.com">hello@tcpclothing.com</a> with your order number and the items you'd like to return. We'll send you the return address and instructions within 1 business day.</p>
          </div>
        </details>
        <details class="faq-item">
          <summary>Who pays for return shipping?</summary>
          <div class="faq-answer">
            <p>Return shipping costs are the customer's responsibility unless the item is faulty or we made an error. We recommend using a tracked service as we cannot be responsible for lost returns.</p>
          </div>
        </details>
        <details class="faq-item">
          <summary>How long does a refund take?</summary>
          <div class="faq-answer">
            <p>Once we receive and inspect your return, we'll process your refund within 5 business days. It may take an additional 3–5 days to appear on your statement depending on your bank.</p>
          </div>
        </details>
        <details class="faq-item">
          <summary>Can I return swimwear?</summary>
          <div class="faq-answer">
            <p>For hygiene reasons, swimwear can only be returned if it is completely unworn and the hygiene sticker is still attached. Swimwear that has been tried on without the hygiene liner cannot be returned.</p>
          </div>
        </details>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="faq-section" id="care">
      <h2>Care Instructions</h2>
      <div class="faq-list">
        <details class="faq-item">
          <summary>How should I wash linen pieces?</summary>
          <div class="faq-answer">
            <p>Machine wash at 30°C on a gentle cycle, or hand wash. Lay flat or hang to dry — avoid tumble drying as linen can shrink. A cool iron while slightly damp will smooth any wrinkles.</p>
          </div>
        </details>
        <details class="faq-item">
          <summary>How do I care for swimwear?</summary>
          <div class="faq-answer">
            <p>Rinse in cold water after each use, especially after swimming in the sea or pool. Hand wash with mild detergent, reshape, and lay flat to dry. Avoid wringing out and never machine wash swimwear.</p>
          </div>
        </details>
        <details class="faq-item">
          <summary>Will the colours fade?</summary>
          <div class="faq-answer">
            <p>Our fabrics are dyed to be colourfast. To maintain vibrancy, wash dark colours inside out in cold water and avoid prolonged sun exposure when wet.</p>
          </div>
        </details>
      </div>
    </section>

  </div>

  <div class="faq-contact-cta">
    <p>Still have questions? We're happy to help.</p>
    <a href="/pages/contact" class="btn btn--primary">Contact Us</a>
  </div>

</div>

{% stylesheet %}
  .faq-page {
    padding: 48px 40px 80px;
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .faq-nav {
    display: flex;
    gap: 8px;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    margin-bottom: 56px;
    padding-bottom: 24px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border, #E8E2DC);
  }

  .faq-nav__link {
    font-size: 0.8125rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 1.5px;
    color: var(--color-muted, #8C8580);
    text-decoration: none;
    padding: 6px 14px;
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border, #E8E2DC);
    border-radius: 2px;
    transition: all 0.15s ease;
  }

  .faq-nav__link:hover {
    color: var(--color-foreground, #141414);
    border-color: var(--color-foreground, #141414);
  }

  .faq-sections {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0;
  }

  .faq-section {
    padding: 48px 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border, #E8E2DC);
  }

  .faq-section h2 {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    font-weight: 400;
    margin-bottom: 24px;
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
  }

  .faq-list {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0;
  }

  .faq-item {
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border, #E8E2DC);
  }

  .faq-item:last-child {
    border-bottom: none;
  }

  .faq-item summary {
    font-size: 0.9375rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    padding: 18px 0;
    cursor: pointer;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
    list-style: none;
    user-select: none;
    color: var(--color-foreground, #141414);
    transition: color 0.15s ease;
  }

  .faq-item summary::-webkit-details-marker {
    display: none;
  }

  .faq-item summary::after {
    content: '+';
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    font-weight: 300;
    color: var(--color-accent, #C2946B);
    flex-shrink: 0;
    margin-left: 16px;
    transition: transform 0.2s ease;
  }

  .faq-item[open] summary::after {
    transform: rotate(45deg);
  }

  .faq-item summary:hover {
    color: var(--color-accent, #C2946B);
  }

  .faq-answer {
    padding: 0 0 20px;
    font-size: 0.9375rem;
    color: var(--color-muted, #8C8580);
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  .faq-answer p {
    margin-bottom: 12px;
  }

  .faq-answer p:last-child {
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  .faq-answer ul {
    padding-left: 20px;
    margin: 12px 0;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 6px;
  }

  .faq-answer a {
    color: var(--color-accent, #C2946B);
    text-decoration: underline;
  }

  .faq-contact-cta {
    margin-top: 64px;
    padding: 48px;
    background: var(--color-bg-subtle, #F7F3EF);
    border-radius: 2px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
    gap: 24px;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .faq-contact-cta p {
    font-size: 1.0625rem;
    font-weight: 400;
    margin: 0;
  }
{% endstylesheet %}

{% schema %}
{
  "name": "FAQ",
  "settings": []
}
{% endschema %}
